                "invention-title": [
                    "Chlorine-containing plastic and red mud coupling value-added co-production and chlorine fixation method and device",
                    "一种含氯塑料与赤泥耦合增值联产及固氯的方法与装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the related technical field of solid waste treatment, and discloses a chlorine-containing plastic and red mud coupling value-added co-production and chlorine fixation method which comprises the following steps: (i) a coupling pyrolysis step: co-pyrolyzing chlorine-containing plastic and red mud, and reacting to obtain solid residues and dechlorinated volatile components; (ii) synthesis of an anti-chlorine catalyst: taking the solid residue as a catalyst carrier, and synthesizing the catalyst with an anti-chlorine effect; and (iii) a value-added co-production step in which the dechlorinated volatile component and the chlorine-resistant catalyst are jointly sent to a fluidized bed reactor, sufficiently reacted and subjected to gas-solid separation, thereby achieving value-added co-production of the final products including the carbon nanotubes, the hydrogen-rich gas, the pyrolytic oil and the ferric chloride. The invention further discloses a corresponding device. According to the invention, the problems of incomplete plastic degradation, low resource utilization efficiency of red mud, chlorine and chloride pollution, high catalyst cost, easy inactivation, low added value of products and the like can be effectively solved, and synergistic degradation and continuous value-added co-production are realized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于固废处理相关技术领域，并公开了一种含氯塑料与赤泥耦合增值联产及固氯的方法，包括：(i)耦合热解步骤，其中将含氯塑料与赤泥共热解，并反应得到固体剩余物和脱氯挥发分；(ii)抗氯催化剂的合成，其中将固体剩余物作为催化剂载体，并合成具有抗氯效果的催化剂；(iii)增值联产步骤，其中将脱氯挥发分和抗氯催化剂共同送至流化床反应器，充分反应并执行气固分离，由此实现最终产物包含碳纳米管、富氢气、热解油和氯化铁的增值联产。本发明还公开了相应的装置。通过本发明，能够有效解决塑料降解不彻底，赤泥资源化利用效率低，氯及氯化物污染，催化剂成本高、易失活，产品附加值较低等问题，并实现协同降解和连续化增值联产。"
                }
            ]
